es. {\{}T{\}}he nocturnal horizontal$\backslash$ntemperature gradient was somewhat different than that reported for$\backslash$nother large cities, and the {\{}UHI{\}} did not decrease with increasing$\backslash$nwind speeds until the wind speeds exceeded 7 m s-1.},
